  "title": "Kitchen Attendant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist the chef / cooks in the preparation and cooking of meals</li>\n  <li>Preparation and setting up of food to be deliver to the wards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the Kitchen equipment is kept clean and food preparation is compliance as accordance to the guideline under MOH / NEA regulations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to read and understand simple English</li>\n  <li>Non-Halal Kitchen</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Working hour</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5.5-day work week; must be willing to work on weekends and public holidays, with rotating shifts (off day on a weekday).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Annual Leave</li>\n  <li>Family Care Leave</li>\n  <li>Medical &amp; Dental</li>\n  <li>AWS and Variable Bonus</li>\n</ul>",
